>> title: Sweet potato cream
>> description: sweat potatoes made into a creamy texture

Boil the @sweet potatoes{2} with skin in some #water with a little bit of @salt{} until done. Use a #pan with a lid{}.

Cut the cooked sweet potatoes and take out the flesh with a #spoon.

Finely chop the @shallots{4}.

Mix the mash with the @smoked bacon{100%gram} and the chopped shallots.

Add @salt{} and @pepper{} to taste.